### Option 3: Blender (No-Code 3D Modeling)

1. Download and install [Blender](https://www.blender.org/)
2. Open Blender and go to **Add > Mesh > Cube**
3. Scale and position the cube to form the house body
4. Add a **Cone** for the roof
5. Use **Edit Mode** to add windows and doors
6. Render with **F12**

